Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.18,0:22:49.18,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}罰を受けし心は
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.82,0:22:53.46,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}夜の迷路へ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.40,0:22:58.50,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}茨の王　赦さず
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.02,0:23:02.45,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}解けめ鎖
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.62,0:23:12.14,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}求めたのは　永遠　埋めたは愛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.91,0:23:21.73,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}穢れ壊れた　僕をみないで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.09,0:23:30.92,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}裂かれた絆　黒きレクイエム
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.31,0:23:40.18,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}ここにこないで　君は知らないで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.57,0:23:47.50,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}絶望の雨が降れる　世界が……
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.55,0:23:48.95,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}今、終わる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.13,0:23:54.60,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}Which Shinetu as a flame in the midst of your palace
